{"tid":1853820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門警方繼續聯絡128名留澳門湖北人要求離境","createTime":"2020-01-31T07:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T07:49:32.000Z","uid":226984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"493bbaf6a8a7626e1ceab40445568230245ef159","tid":1853820,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"澳門警方繼續嘗試聯絡仍然留在澳門的湖北人離境。警方表示，截至中午，仍有184名湖北人未離開澳門，當中來自武漢市的有79人。剔除已入住指定觀察點的36人，和入境澳門已超過14日的20人，仍需聯絡128名留在澳門的湖北人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，因應內地旅客量大幅減少，澳門當局宣布明天會暫停部分巴士線，以免資源浪費。受影響的4條巴士線，都是由關閘廣場開出的快線，分別是到市中心轉車站、景點旅遊塔等，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505859-20200131.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505859-20200131.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=21800329\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505859-20200131.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ce36e3e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505859-20200131.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"990d6ff616b7b1ea0eeea462560d8d27bc5ac8a4","tid":1853820,"uid":261937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:38:58.000Z","msg":"賀一誠有料到"},{"pid":"fc0d9800250cf35ad710a76827bce4ce3616bddb","tid":1853820,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:49:32.000Z","msg":"港共澳門都不如 <br />\n借位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗疫不忘抗爭</span></span><br />\n希望大家幫p牌推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解答到 國際關係 海洋法庭制裁警暴<br />\n呢啲議題 <br />\n唔好比肺炎spin開左 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地仲未光復到香港！</span></span><br />\n一齊收港共支共皮<br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉高汁分析 點光復香港<br />\n<a h